snippet.title: Puzzle Wizards Early Access Trailer
snippet.description: Puzzle Wizards https://puzzlewizards.net/ is a new co-op puzzle MMO game from the creators of Puzzle Pirates. Play three puzzles to harvest, craft and battle with friends to restore and decorate your village, spiff up your wizard's clothes and rebuild the world with your Wizard Order!
